        <x>134</x>
        <y>40</y>
        <width>251</width>
        <height>171</height>
       </rect>
      </property>
      <property name="markdown">
       <string>ION-Sim: A framework for interacting with different scenarios characteristic of
intraoperative monitoring sessions in supra, infra-tentorial, and spinal
surgery. The learning process is suggested with a gradual approach to
multimodal monitoring challenges. Simulation in individual modalities allows
acquiring sufficient familiarity to later face the problems that arise in a
real scenario.

</string>
      </property>
     </widget>
     <widget class="QLabel" name="labelDateTime_2">
      <property name="geometry">
