    <widget class="QWidget" name="tab_ANESTH">
     <attribute name="title">
      <string>ANESTH</string>
     </attribute>
     <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit_16">
      <property name="geometry">
       <rect>
        <x>132</x>
        <y>40</y>
        <width>251</width>
        <height>171</height>
       </rect>
      </property>
      <property name="markdown">
       <string>ION-Sim: Anesthesia control module with ECG, Arterial Pressure, O2 saturation,
Heart Rate with R-R, SDNN and RMSSD, Respiratory Cycle, TCI infusion control of
Propofol, Remifentanil and Ketamine, independent control of Sevoflurane.
Adaptation of patient's metadata with age, sex, heght and weight with
calculated BMI and LBM.

</string>
      </property>
     </widget>
