       </rect>
      </property>
      <property name="markdown">
       <string>ION-Sim: BAEP module. Simulation of the brainstem response activating the
cochlear nuclei and pontine structures involved, following unilateral acoustic
stimulation in alternating mode to get information from both sides of the
afferent auditory pathway.

</string>
      </property>
     </widget>
